channel.title: How do i run 562 client on 525 server?
channel.description:
How do i run khanz 562 ipchanger on pur3zscape 525 source/server? 562 clients are the only clients that work on my windows 7, every 525 client say's this in the command promt window if i run it:
Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: client Caused by: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: client at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run(Unknown Source) at java.security.AccessController.doPrivileged(Native Method) at java.net.URLClassLoader.findClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) Could not find the main class: client. Program will exit. Press any key to continue...
, but there are no good 562 sources. (with clipping, without errors,npc combat,with :: commands,...) If you know a good 562 source with all this stuffs, plzz give me a link. Otherwise, tell me how to run a 562 client with a 525 server/source Plz, keep it simple, i am a noob in this things :p
